snippet.title: Let's play QuizWitz!
snippet.description: A browser-­based party quiz game players can control using their smartphone, tablet, laptop, or any device that supports a browser. It’s platform-­independent and will come with its own community platform where players can collect, create and publish their own question packs in relation to their own interests. The game will have a vintage feel and will come to life thanks to a witty quiz host and jazzy music and sounds. People who love to create quizzes will see theirs played around the world.
